{UTF-8}
Asset Value = INTEG ( Investment - Depreciation, 500 )
	~ Dollar
	~ 折旧/衰减稳态：固定投资与折旧平衡，资产价值收敛到稳态。设备/资产/库存衰减通用结构。
	|

Investment = 50
	~ Dollar/Year
	~ 固定投资率（可改为政策变量）
	|

Depreciation = Asset Value / Useful Life
	~ Dollar/Year
	~ 折旧=资产/使用寿命
	|

Useful Life = 20
	~ Year
	~ 资产使用寿命
	|

Steady State Value = Investment * Useful Life
	~ Dollar
	~ 理论稳态值=投资率×使用寿命
	|

INITIAL TIME = 0
	~ Year
	~	|

FINAL TIME = 80
	~ Year
	~	|

TIME STEP = 0.5
	~ Year
	~	|

SAVEPER = TIME STEP
	~ Year
	~	|

